summary: This Mod adds a new Island for you to discover!
descriptionHtml:
LORE
Uliric Ermaraan founded this island in 2E201, and named the island Ermaraan.
Imperials have occupied the Land, can you take them down? free the land of the Empire.


Version: 
ALPHA v1.0

How to get to Ermaraan: 
Travel to riverwood, ther you must go to the little island and find the statue click on int and you will be at Ermaraan!

Known bugs:

The Statue might be gone while entering Eramaraan, but you can get back to skyrim by opening the console and enter \"coc riverwood)
